precis:
Amendment (SCHEDULE No. 921) to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS providing for
the use of sucrose acetate isobutyrate, as a density adjusting agent or
stabilizer in citrus flavoured and spruce flavoured beverages at a
maximum level of 300 ppm.
